| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4831 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2b5dbe9a-99e4-5af4-b40e-26813e1384a4"
